                            <comment id="436748" author="JIRAUSER18021" created="Wed, 27 Nov 2024 10:20:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reporter solved the problem and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-523&quot; title=&quot;add proper documentation for replace_nids command&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUDOC-523&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUDOC-523&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has been created to address lctl replace_nids documentation changes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="322450" author="rs1" created="Wed, 12 Jan 2022 15:28:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I successfully used the writeconf method to move the OSTs to different servers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="322014" author="adilger" created="Fri, 7 Jan 2022 04:21:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is some brief description of the &lt;tt&gt;replace_nids&lt;/tt&gt; command in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-523&quot; title=&quot;add proper documentation for replace_nids command&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUDOC-523&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11846&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and a request to the author of that command to provide a separate &lt;tt&gt;lctl-replace_nids.8&lt;/tt&gt; man page that has a more complete description of that command, and preferably with some usage examples.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
